## 1. Vision, Soul & Core Values

- **Motto:** "Logistics with Soul."
- **Core Values:** Gratitude | Curiosity | Creation
- **Focus:** E-commerce Small Parcel Logistics for 3PLs and brands
  shipping 500+ orders/day.
- **Phases:**
  - Phase 1 — Rating & Billing Engine (current)
  - Phase 2 — Client-Facing Billing Suite & Analytics
  - Phase 3 — Full Warehouse Management System (WMS)

---

## 2. Naming Conventions (The "Cactus Map")

These are non-negotiable. Inconsistency here causes bugs that are
very hard to trace.

- **Project Files & Folders:** Always `kebab-case`
  - ✅ `database-setup.sql`, `rating-engine.ts`, `seed-data.sql`
  - ❌ `DatabaseSetup.sql`, `ratingEngine.ts`

- **Database Tables & Columns:** Always `snake_case`
  - ✅ `org_id`, `shipment_ledger`, `final_merchant_rate`
  - ❌ `orgId`, `ShipmentLedger`, `FinalMerchantRate`

- **Application Code (TypeScript/JavaScript):** Always `camelCase`
  for variables and functions
  - ✅ `finalMerchantRate`, `calculateMarkup()`, `orgId`
  - ❌ `final_merchant_rate`, `CalculateMarkup()`

- **React Components & TypeScript Types/Interfaces:** `PascalCase`
  - ✅ `ShipmentCard`, `OrgType`, `RateCardProps`
  - ❌ `shipmentCard`, `org_type`

- **Constants:** `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE`
  - ✅ `MAX_RELOAD_AMOUNT`, `DEFAULT_TERMS_DAYS`

